deftms ~>>>MORSE 'Assemblage of FE matrices into a global matrix
Only the non zero coefficients of the matrix are stored
LPLIGN(i) i diagonal coefficient pointer on the vector MORSE
and by extension LPLIGN(0)=0'
variable muet DATE 'date of creation of the TMS' reel2  ;
variable muet NUTD 'number of the descriptor array TD' entier ; 
variable NBLIMO 'line number of the matrix MORSE'  entier ;
variable LPMORS 'even number of words to point on MORSE' entier ;
tableau  LPLIGN(0..NBLIMO)
'pointer on MORSE of each diagonal coefficient & LPLIGN(0)=0' entier ;
tableau  LPCOLO(1..LPLIGN(NBLIMO))
'pointer on MORSE of the number of column of each non zero coefficient' entier ;
tableau  MORSE(1..LPLIGN(NBLIMO)) 'coefficients of the matrix MORSE' reel2  ;
fintms ;
